author: NEWSDAY.COM
title: 'Grapple at the Garden' to take place Nov. 29 at MSG
text:
Madison Square Garden will host the fourth annual "Grapple at the Garden" on Nov. 29.
22 schools, including power programs Cornell, Nebraska, Illinois and Northwestern as well as Stony Brook, Hofstra, LIU Post and SUNY Famingdale will participate in the dual-meet tournament.
The meet will also feature the best New York City high school wrestlers from the PSAL, CHSAA and independent school against other in-stare wrestlers.
Tickets start at $20.00 and can be purchased online at www.thegarden.com, all Ticketmaster locations and the Madison Square Garden box office.
